Classes
Class
Description
PokeAnswerAPI
Class used to map the initial list of the Pokemon retrieved from the call to the API
PokeCall
Class used to map the response of the API
Pokemon
Class designed to be mapped for the final response of each call to the API which contains any "Pokemon" object
PokemonListController
This class acts as the controller for this application.
PokemonMapper
Class designed to map the items contained on the list of Pokemon received by the API response (PokeAnswerAPI) to the class Pokemon, which is later showed to the client
PokeRepository
Class designed to act as the repository of the application
PokeResponse
Class to show to the client after being mapped from PokeCall
PokeService
Class designed to act as service for the application

Main of the application
